530
00:54:32.100 --> 00:54:33.790
Oh astaga!

531
00:54:36.130 --> 00:54:40.330
Astaga, dia sangat lucu.

532
00:54:40.330 --> 00:54:44.280
Astaga, dia bukan tipeku, tapi...

533
00:54:45.570 --> 00:54:48.780
Hai, oppa. Aku sedang dalam perjalanan.

